<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10132877>
    dc:description "Figure 5. A, Hymedesmia (Hymedesmia) rathlinia sp. nov. A, large acanthostyle; B, small acanthostyle; C, base of large acanthostyle; D, ends of ectosomal spicule; E, chelae. Scale bars: 10 Mm. B, Hymedesmia (Hymedesmia) rathlinia sp. nov., surface, undisturbed, covered in silt. C, Hymedesmia (Hymedesmia) rathlinia sp. nov., surface, with silt removed." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10132877/files/figure.png" ;
